{
  "stem": "812.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And on her bicycle, she went to her clients and was able to make a living with her new profession as a manicurist, pedicurist, and masseuse.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My brother Al and I, we moved to Bussum, as I had said.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were in this Youth Aliyah home with the Birnbaums, who were in charge of this home where some 25 or so children lived.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Most of these children came from camps without their parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were orphans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were in this home in preparation, actually, to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were taught Hebrew in the home, and it was a-- an Orthodox upbringing at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And our secular studies were in a Montessori school in Bussum.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Montessori-- I don't know if you're familiar with the Montessori system.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was an ideal situation for us, children who have had no education whatsoever prior.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Here I was, 11 years old, starting in Dutch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I never had spoken Dutch and I didn't know Dutch, and we started in Dutch in the Montessori school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were in a large area, all of us in one big room with a few teachers, and we all learned at our own pace.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It worked out well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we lived very comfortably in this home in Bussum.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And it was actually a wonderful life, except that we missed not being with my mother, and I got very homesick many, many times.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My mother did come to visit us once a week.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the following week, my brother and I would visit her over the weekend in-- or just for the day, for Sunday, in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
